Package: python-midolman-nova
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-openvswitch
Description: OpenStack plugin for Midolman.
 Midolman implements OpenStack Nova's network API to serve as its network
 service provider.

Package: midolman-agent-common
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: configuration(dependency package) for the Midolman agent.
 Midolman agent allows full control of Midolman agents servers.

Package: midolman-agent-bin
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-midolman-nova
Description: Net agent service scripts for Midolman.
 Midonet agent service that performs local network setups and teardowns.

